"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/02/130224.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1486729","time":"2019-9-2 18:02","userId":"soviet","userName":"神之迷徒","userSign":"(崩坏の节操)","message":"漫无目的的话不如直接选择OVA的排行榜就行了<br><a href=\"http://bgm.tv/index/22646\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://bgm.tv/index/22646</a>   <br>你喜欢的元素（萌，燃，励志，小黄段子。。。），你的欣赏角度（剧情，画风，作画？）才是绝对一部OVA你值不值得看。OVA佳作大多并不是整体实力强大，而且有特别亮的亮点，是要讲究缘分的，比如所谓的OVA双壁就是看设定（设定现在看依旧是顶级的，你甚至能看到攻壳机动队1995复刻它的分镜，但是其他未必你能接受）。上面推荐条子的OVA，但是你知道押井守吗？不知道恐怕就很难接受了那样的演出风格（而且OVA有些单元剧也一般，旧版就5,6集好看，新版5集以后高能）。OVA的STAFF自由度比较高，玩得比较欢腾，实验性比较高。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/02/130224.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1486730","time":"2019-9-2 18:04","userId":"soviet","userName":"神之迷徒","userSign":"","message":"大多数OVA都是导演玩票性质的，只有AIC的OVA有系统性的开放，可以入坑。看OVA就如掏二手书店那样，时常能够挖掘出一些私货，通灵公主，怪力少女，恶魔战士，恶魔的新娘 兰之组曲，伊利亚：杰拉姆动画版，帝都物语，如果在梦里遇见你 OVA等等6分左右的OVA，有的是剧情，构图，人设，设定，演出，对的上眼就会很愉悦。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/02/130224.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1486741","time":"2019-9-2 18:31","userId":"soviet","userName":"神之迷徒","userSign":"(崩坏の节操)","message":"<img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/91/f4/130224_aP044.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/91/f4/130224_US6G3.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/91/f4/130224_DG63m.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/91/f4/130224_Jo9m9.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>相比现在需要路人/建筑/场景就是建模后的复制黏贴，旧时代的构图有些设计元素很重。像第一张图片，通过对两人色度的处理，妈妈与DoReMi的两代人隔阂就表现出来了，需要什么剧情？需要什么台词？不及这张图片顶用。骑马那张是出气筒的演出，现在画面比越做越宽，当年的出气筒就反其道而行之，月光集束，周边黑屏屏蔽掉周围敌人，营造出面对千万敌人包围中公主骑士两个人世界的氛围，这叫“情景合一”？我就觉得出气筒牛逼，一个镜头顶人家一部片——在OVA整体平均并不是都很突出的情况下，剧情好，配乐棒，资金充足作画棒就那么几部，大多情况下，你要在一堆5-7分的缺陷片中找到你喜欢的，你需要考虑喜欢什么元素后再入OVA坑比较好。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/16/331630.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1486866","time":"2019-9-2 21:45","userId":"wudiangongyuan","userName":"五点共圆","userSign":"","message":"谈得好！我确实越来越能感受出崎统的伟大了。。。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/26/442668.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1486905","time":"2019-9-2 23:06","userId":"442668","userName":"除以零","userSign":"","message":"我看OVA主要是喜欢赛璐珞的风格，那种胶片上色后有种通透感，看着很舒服，现在数码动画色彩更丰富特效更强大后反而觉得光污染。而且那时的原画大佬云集，画功扎实，虽然很多OVA剧情都一言难尽但是看着画面确实享受。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/02/130224.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1486742","time":"2019-9-2 18:36","userId":"soviet","userName":"神之迷徒","userSign":"(崩坏の节操)","message":"<img src=\"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/91/f4/130224_dNqF8.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>百度坑了，补图","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/82/318251.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1486840","time":"2019-9-2 20:34","userId":"h751984871","userName":"751984871","userSign":"(动画党，喜补不喜追，偶尔碰下已/快完结漫画和无内购游戏 ...)","message":"在补JOJO之前试着考古了下这个。<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/55033\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://bgm.tv/subject/55033</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1486849","time":"2019-9-2 20:58","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"","message":"好像有点意思，mark一下，谢谢分享"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/16/331630.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1486848","time":"2019-9-2 20:58","userId":"wudiangongyuan","userName":"五点共圆","userSign":"(科气严重，缺乏妹子)","message":"押井守ova全家桶。强烈推荐条子新ova、祖先大人万万岁。<br>出崎统ova，我看得还是不足，但是基本可以确定都是好作品。。。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/16/331630.jpg","floor":"#14-1","id":"1487039","time":"2019-9-3 10:08","userId":"wudiangongyuan","userName":"五点共圆","userSign":"","message":"加上一些作画片，起源之类的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/84/438454.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1486901","time":"2019-9-2 22:52","userId":"438454","userName":"Nicho Deci","userSign":"","message":"高山文彦：0080；<br>梅津泰臣：a kite<br>押井守不用说了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/95/409538.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1487025","time":"2019-9-3 08:44","userId":"kagaminori","userName":"kagami","userSign":"(思い立ったが吉日)","message":"机动警察新ova 祖先大人万万岁+1<br>补充黄金小子和幽幻怪社","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/99/409941.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1487129","time":"2019-9-3 13:21","userId":"409941","userName":"Nevermore","userSign":"","message":"机动警察新ova、祖先大人万万岁+2。押井全家桶还有<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/4188\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">天使之卵</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/ep/131588\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">迷宫物件</a>。<br>一般所称的第一部OVA是1983年的《DALLOS》，所以70年代也就没有了吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/21.gif\" smileid=\"60\" alt=\"(bgm44)\">。<br>很多知名TV衍生的ova也大多是名作，90年代主要是高达“三八”、超时空要塞Plus和浪客剑心追忆篇吧，这些也基本在排行榜中都榜上有名。<br>私心推荐<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/37012\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">机甲猎兵</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/40391\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">DOWNLOAD 阿弥陀佛诗歌</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/44521\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">灵猫</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/27213\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">战区88</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/23618\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">天使特警</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/33219\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">无限地带23</a>、<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/30491\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">奥美帝III</a>。<br>至于这部据传被欧美OVA迷认为是“80年代最差劲的动画”，<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/subject/67732\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">食心物体X</a>，确实很糟，但是烂作烂到一定程度反而会是别样味道的cult片，虽说慎入，但偶尔也可以试毒一下<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401529.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1487221","time":"2019-9-3 18:13","userId":"isleeper","userName":"JOB","userSign":"","message":"老OVA就看过 飞跃颠峰 和 浪客剑心 ，就推荐你没标记的《浪客剑心 追忆篇》吧。此片受众较广，bgm OVA Top1，属于TV的前传，看过TV一两集再补为佳，没看过也不太影响。个人认为此片全方面都比较优秀，战斗画面，人物塑造，背景音乐可以比过现在大多数作品，且此片可以找到优质资源。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/67/366797.jpg","floor":"#19","id":"1487335","time":"2019-9-3 21:46","userId":"ciooc","userName":"CiooC","userSign":"(“我如朝露降人间”)","message":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/60822536/answer/812101553\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/60822536/answer/812101553</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/69/246935.jpg","floor":"#19-1","id":"1488475","time":"2019-9-6 19:16","userId":"246935","userName":"llxl2","userSign":"","message":"艾蕾推荐那个感觉也可以"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/67/366797.jpg","floor":"#19-2","id":"1488479","time":"2019-9-6 19:33","userId":"ciooc","userName":"CiooC","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">llxl2</span> 说: 艾蕾推荐那个感觉也可以</q></div>嗯  我见前面有人提过了就没放链接"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/69/246935.jpg","floor":"#19-3","id":"1488485","time":"2019-9-6 20:10","userId":"246935","userName":"llxl2","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">CiooC</span> 说: 嗯&nbsp;&nbsp;我见前面有人提过了就没放链接</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">他用了替换我没看出来<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/67/366797.jpg","floor":"#19-4","id":"1488488","time":"2019-9-6 20:29","userId":"ciooc","userName":"CiooC","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">llxl2</span> 说: 他用了替换我没看出来</q></div>话说子回复里的b38是怎么打出来的？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/69/246935.jpg","floor":"#19-5","id":"1489346","time":"2019-9-8 06:01","userId":"246935","userName":"llxl2","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">CiooC</span> 